{"title":"有这样一个筑路工地（二首）","authors":["田耕"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":8,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"有这样一个筑路工地（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田耕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帐篷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是因为有仿宋字的帐篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誊在带格的原野上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有原野上的帐篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被小鸟读出的平仄的诗行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有了工地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了帐篷无韵的句式里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深奥的意象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是在一条条路装订成册的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集子里，城市和楼房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被发表了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工间休息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说，忘记思念才是好筑路工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以这一刻是属于她的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以这一刻她属于我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静地静静地躺下去躺下去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让干热风撩起油衬衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撩起爱撩起思念；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，剪一段路做信笺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做信笺写上文字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复印在旋转的旋转的车轮上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄给城市寄给她；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用红绿灯做标点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把每一条街写成自然段。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上班路上，她会读懂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她会读懂。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}